# Single source of truth for the cloud environment and default model every
# routine deploys with.
#
# The deploy process — the `deploy-routine-changes` skill (interactive) and the
# `deploy-routines` GHA prompt (when its CI token is unblocked) — reads these
# from here and sets `job_config.ccr.environment_id` and
# `job_config.ccr.session_context.model` on every RemoteTrigger create/update.
# Pin each here once; never repeat the value elsewhere.
#
# CLAUDE_SONNET_MODEL_ID is the DEFAULT model. A routine that needs a different
# model keeps an explicit `model:` line in its frontmatter (which wins); absent
# that line, the deploy sets the model to this value. issue-solver runs via GHA
# (`.github/workflows/issue-solver.yml`), not the deploy skill, so that workflow
# reads CLAUDE_SONNET_MODEL_ID from this file directly.
#
# The environment's CONTENTS — GH_OWNER, GH_TOKEN, and other secrets — live ONLY
# in the cloud environment (claude.ai), never in this repo. This file pins WHICH
# environment, not WHAT is in it.
#
# Format: KEY=VALUE, one per line. Read with:
#   grep -m1 '^ENVIRONMENT_ID=' routines/_common/deploy.config | cut -d= -f2 | tr -d '\r'
ENVIRONMENT_ID=env_01GVXvvN64GtSjsfhychXy7m
CLAUDE_SONNET_MODEL_ID=claude-sonnet-5
